@TomSweeneyRedHat I was actually looking into this a bit a while back after noticing [this issue](https://github.com/containers/buildah/issues/1936#issuecomment-605285921) related to ARG/ENV handling.

I noticed that all the existing ENVs and ARGs are getting thrown into the step env here https://github.com/openshift/imagebuilder/blob/e307568568533c4afccdf7b56df7b4493e4e9a7b/builder.go#L336-L338. My thought was to add deduplication and priority there, but I never got the chance to implement it.

Hope this helps!
